## ðŸ“Š Dashboard Features
- **KPIs Overview**: Total Revenue, No. of Transactions, Avg. Sales per Transaction  
- **Sales Trends**: Line charts showing sales over time  
- **Top Products**: Best-selling coffee types & categories  
- **Location Analysis**: Revenue distribution across different stores  
- **Customer Insights**: Time-based purchase behavior (morning vs. evening sales)  
- **Filters & Slicers**: Interactive controls for product type, date range, and store location  

